The paper discusses the analysis of online forums, specifically Reddit, which falls under the category of social media analysis. Therefore, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of computational methods to extract information from the structure and dynamics of the system, which could fall under cs.CY (Computational Geometry), cs.SD (Software Engineering), or cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper discusses the practical applications of understanding online forum behavior, which could fall under cs.SOC (Computational Social Science).
